abstract: A detergent brand tries to fill a need with what it hopes is an “efficient way to clean up your online profile.”
snippet: A detergent brand tries to fill a need with what it hopes is an “efficient way to clean up your online profile.”
lead_paragraph: You there, you who dressed as a sexy panther this Halloween, and are now clicking through the weekend’s photos on Facebook. (The ones of you clutching a vodka and snarling like a kittycat are particularly nice.) Your boss, your exes and your mother are probably looking at them this morning, too. What’s a hungover cat to do?

headline.main: An Application to Help Scrub Those Regrettable Photos From Facebook
